<section class="blog--post desktop-only">
<div><p>Spring Boot 1.3.4 has been released and is available now from <a href="https://repo.spring.io/release">repo.spring.io</a> and <a href="https://search.maven.org/#search%7Cga%7C1%7Cg%3A%22org.springframework.boot%22">Maven Central</a>. </p>
