<h2 class="blog--title">
<a href="/blog/2016/05/06/spring-framework-4-3-rc2-4-2-6-and-3-2-17-available-now">Spring Framework 4.3 RC2, 4.2.6 and 3.2.17 available now</a>
</h2>
<header class="meta-data--container">
<div class="meta-data--item desktop-only">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon releases"></div>
<a class="category" href="/blog/category/releases">Releases</a>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<img class="meta-data--icon" src="https://gravatar.com/avatar/33d0963a20138828608f3f61927545b8?s=20&amp;d=mm" />
<a class="author" href="/team/snicoll">Stéphane Nicoll</a>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon calendar"></div>
<time class="date" pubdate="" datetime="2016-05-06 13:59:44.06">May 6, 2016</time>
</div>
<div class="meta-data--item">
<div class="meta-data--icon icon blog-icon comments"></div>
<a class="comments" data-disqus-identifier="2492" href="/blog/2016/05/06/spring-framework-4-3-rc2-4-2-6-and-3-2-17-available-now#disqus_thread">
</a></div>
</header>
<section class="blog--post desktop-only">
<div><p>It is my pleasure to announce that the Spring Framework <a href="https://jira.spring.io/secure/ReleaseNote.jspa?projectId=10000&amp;version=15460">4.2.6</a> and <a href="https://jira.spring.io/secure/ReleaseNote.jspa?projectId=10000&amp;version=15518">3.2.17</a> maintenance releases <a href="https://projects.spring.io/spring-framework">are available now</a>. We also released <a href="https://jira.spring.io/secure/ReleaseNote.jspa?projectId=10000&amp;version=15487">the second release candidate of the 4.3 line</a>.</p>
<p>4.3 RC2 contains many refinements and fixes, especially in the web framework area. We are about to finalize 4.3 with a scheduled GA in early June. Preparations towards merging 5.0 features into master will happen right afterwards, with a first 5.0 milestone expected in July.</p>
<p><a href="https://projects.spring.io/spring-framework/">Project Page</a> | <a href="https://github.com/spring-projects/spring-framework">GitHub</a> | <a href="https://jira.spring.io/browse/SPR">Issues</a> | <a href="https://docs.spring.io/spring-framework/docs/current/spring-framework-reference/htmlsingle/">Documentation</a></p>
</div>
</section>
